overview: The construction work to build the Kg. Latah Sports Complex is stopped when contract workers come across the pharaoh's mummy's coffin. When it is opened, the pharaoh's mummy has risen and disturbed them. Ajin, Jamilah, Eton, Mansur and Din try to combat the evil work of the pharaoh's mummy in various ways. The situation becomes chaotic when the mummy also raised ghosts from the grave to disturb the villagers and Jamilah’s disappearance becomes a mystery.
title: Kampung Latah… The Mummy
